    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual. The high-revving valvetrain has been meticulously maintained with a recent Double VANOS overhaul and shim-and-bucket valve adjustment. Handling is sharpened via Bilstein dampers and reinforced rear subframe mounting points, ensuring structural rigidity under high lateral loads. The variable M-differential provides exceptional traction and torque vectoring. While the exterior reflects its history as a dedicated driver\u2019s car with minor cosmetic patina, the mechanical synchronization is flawless, offering a visceral, analog experience for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
