      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained luxury sedan that perfectly bridges the gap between performance and daily utility. The exterior features a deep, lustrous finish, showing only the minor, superficial character marks consistent with careful ownership. Inside, you'll find a smoke-free cabin with supple leather seating, a crystal-clear infotainment display, and a panoramic sunroof that operates flawlessly. Every button and switch functions as intended, including the dual-zone climate control and premium sound system. Under the hood, the engine is clean and responsive, benefited by a documented history of synthetic oil changes and a recent comprehensive multi-point inspection. The tires have excellent tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. Complete with a full set of service records and two sets of keys, this vehicle offers a refined driving experience that is ready for its next chapter.",
