      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so you can count on it for all your upcoming adventures. It runs smooth and looks great\u2014perfect for someone looking for a reliable daily driver without the brand-new price tag. Come take it for a spin, I\u2019d love to see it go to a good home!",
